    And much more input types ...

    Considerable:
    <ol>
        <li>{{{ htmlCode text="<fieldset>" }}} to group formula elements</li>
        <li>{{{ htmlCode text="<progess>" }}} show progress for the form</li>
        <li>{{{ htmlCode text="tabindex" }}} for the tab sequence</li>
        <li>{{{ htmlCode text="required" }}}</li>
        <li>valid input? show it the user</li>
        <li>{{{ htmlCode text="<datalist>" }}} to list suggestions</li>
    </ol>

